summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 22W, Page 75 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone Block 12 of B.F. Day's First Addition to the City of Seattle, the properties bounded by N. Bowdoin Place, North 39th, Phinney Avenue North and Dayton Avenue North from Residential Multi-Family, Lowrise 3 (L3) Zone to Residential Single Family 5000 (SF 5000) Zone. (Petition of Kathleen Jay Ward, et al.; C.F. No. 292806).
